item.title: Eva Victor and Adele Romanski Want More Mental Health Coordinators on Set: “You Never Know When Something’s Gonna F*** Someone Up”
item.description: The duo spoke about Edinburgh International Film Festival’s opening night film ‘Sorry, Baby’ on Saturday at a session hosted by comedian Rose Matafeo.
